col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4',0,1,1602),('<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/icons/colourful-icons/screen-shot-2018-04-12-at-2.30.22-pm.png\" style=\"width: 75px; height: 72px;\" />Google Calendar Syncing</strong></span></p>','col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4',0,2,1602),('<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/icons/colourful-icons/screen-shot-2018-04-12-at-2.36.16-pm.png\" style=\"width: 75px; height: 74px;\" />Resource Manager</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4',0,3,1602),('','col-xs-12',0,1,1603),('<p><iframe allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/S6vmPuDuuOg\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1605),('<p><strong>Rating</strong>: 5/5</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Challenge&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Myself, fellow guide and good friend had recently taken over the Rafting company &ldquo;Kaituna Cascades&rdquo;&nbsp;located in Okere Falls &ndash; Rotorua . We had both been working there for over ten years and have watched&nbsp;the ways of running a business and always been taking notes on how to improve sales and make it&nbsp;easier for clients to book rafting tours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So one of the first things we did was to upgrade our website as online bookings is the way of the&nbsp;future! We needed a &ldquo;book now&rdquo; button and a booking system behind the scenes to make our life way&nbsp;easier &ndash; so we paired up with the Whyte Waters Group, and they set us up with their Real Time&nbsp;Booking System (RTBS).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our super friendly and knowledgeable local rep made the whole thing really easy and we were away.&nbsp;The system is easy to use and takes away all of the paper work. More importantly our potential clients&nbsp;browsing our website could now hit the book now button and complete the booking online without&nbsp;hassle &ndash; saving us lengthy phone calls, confirming the booking instantly and saving everyone time!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The nature of our business is relatively high volume and mostly last minute online bookings, and as the&nbsp;name suggests &ndash; the Real time booking system keeps everything up to date &ldquo;real time&rdquo; and makes day&nbsp;to day running of the business smooth and simple!&nbsp;Kaituna Cascades would love to give a shout out to Whyte Waters and the RTBS and highly<br />\r\nrecommend using the system to increase and capture sales &ndash; while making life simple and easy.</p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1638),('<p><strong>Rating</strong>: 5/5<br />\r\n<strong>Partnering</strong> <strong>Since</strong>: 10 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Challenge&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our partnership with RTBS has been hugely beneficial to our business. Back in the early days the &ldquo;Black Book&rdquo; proved time and again invaluable to us, the stunning presentation of this was far superior to anything else on the market and still is. I remember the excitement just days after our first publication; a family of 10 adults booked via reception. This, our first advertisement turned to gold for us and remains today one of the very few print runs we invest in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I always enjoyed the visits by David (and more recently Blair) with news of the incredible&nbsp;RTBS system which was being developed by his team... and then it WAS. And it was exactly as good as David had described.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Initially I used this solely as a live booking system for my website, then 2 years ago began&nbsp;using RTBS as my entire booking system which was life changing and time saving; the always&nbsp;at fingertips help from clever ladies Becky &amp; Dot, made this transition seamless.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This summer was yet another break-through for us, using the agent network for live bookings from local accommodation providers and the i-SITE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lake Wanaka i-SITE is one of the busiest in the country, for the i-SITE staff to book us live&nbsp;has been a 2-fold bonus. For them, a quicker turnaround of clients, for us it has saved on&nbsp;hundreds of phone calls. The txt alert is perfect and being able to remotely change&nbsp;availability or any number of parameters is awesome; up to date payment gateways, xero&nbsp;interface (haven&rsquo;t quite taken the plunge with that yet but started using xero in&nbsp;preparation), all brilliant.</p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1639),('','col-xs-12',0,1,1640),('<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/whytewater/termsnconditions/terms-and-conditions-a5-email-version2-3.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 1277px;\" /></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1710),('<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/whytewater/termsnconditions/terms-and-conditions-a5-email-version2-4.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 1277px;\" /></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1711),('<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/whytewater/termsnconditions/terms-and-conditions-a5-email-version2-5.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 1277px;\" /></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1712),('<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/whytewater/termsnconditions/terms-and-conditions-a5-email-version2-6.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 1277px;\" /></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1713),('<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/whytewater/termsnconditions/terms-and-conditions-a5-email-version2-7.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 1277px;\" /></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1714),('<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/library/whytewater/termsnconditions/terms-and-conditions-a5-email-version2-8.jpg\" style=\"width: 900px; height: 1277px;\" /></p>','col-xs-12',0,1,1715),('<p>&nbsp; &nbs